    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The UnitOfAssurance package is accepted for submission to the regulatory dossier. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; six were identified as epistemic gaps and flagged as not-assessed. The overall credibility assessment outcome is Not Accepted for regulatory use — the model does not meet the required credibility levels for Class III VAD absolute hemolysis prediction — however the package itself is accepted as a complete and conformant evidence artifact under ProfileMinimal. The declared signatureAlg (ed25519) is recorded for audit traceability.",
